Dear all,

'Scholarshoppe' has been inaugurated today and they will start their full
fledged operations within 34 days. The shop has a wide range of branded
products with great discounts. They have only a few products which are
readily available. You can give orders for other products and they will
deliver it to you in a few days time. They also take bulk orders for all
the products like T Shirts, Bags etc which can also be customized. The
working hours will be from 11 AM to 9:30 PM everyday.

